3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with color transformations in images, which is a key aspect of multimedia processing. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the construction of invariants using a multiple integration framework, which is a common technique in machine learning. 
5. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper deals with the construction of invariants, which is a key area of information theory.
